This comes from the Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System (BRFSS) from the CDC.  This is the percentage of respondents between that responded Divorced, Widowed or Separated to the following question "Are you: (marital status)".  Other responses included Married, Never Married, A member of an unmarried couple or refused.
